[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Restore Original Constructors in COSParser**  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Revert the removal of the three public constructors in `COSParser.java` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m143[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m181[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This restores compatibility with all existing callers [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`FDFParser`, [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDFParser`, tests, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, eliminating the “constructor cannot be applied” errors. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Remove Erroneous Private Scan Methods and Duplicate Imports**  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Delete the two new private methods `[0m[1;35mparsePDFHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mparseFDFHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat were added at lines ~[0m[1;36m140[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m200[0m[39m. They duplicate the existing protected methods [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand collide on signature.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the duplicate `import java.nio.charset.StandardCharsets;` [0m[1;39m([0m[39monly a [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msingle import is needed if used[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Introduce Configurable Header Lookup Range**  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add a new instance field to `COSParser` [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `private long [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheaderLookupRange;`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and a static default constant:  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public static final String SYSPROP_[0m[1;33mHEAD[0m[39mER_LOOKUP_RANGE =[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[32m"org.apache.pdfbox.pdfparser.headerLookupRange"[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static final long DEFAULT_[0m[1;33mHEAD[0m[39mER_LOOKUP_RANGE = [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the existing `[0m[1;35minit[0m[1;39m([0m[39mStreamCacheCreateFunction[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method, after reading [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`SYSPROP_EOFLOOKUPRANGE`, also read `SYSPROP_[0m[1;33mHEAD[0m[39mER_LOOKUP_RANGE`:[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     String headerRangeProp = [0m[1;35mSystem.getProperty[0m[1;39m([0m[39mSYSPROP_[0m[1;33mHEAD[0m[39mER_LOOKUP_RANGE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mheaderRangeProp != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         headerLookupRange = [0m[1;35mLong.parseLong[0m[1;39m([0m[39mheaderRangeProp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         headerLookupRange = DEFAULT_[0m[1;33mHEAD[0m[39mER_LOOKUP_RANGE;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This makes the header-scan limit configurable [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault = [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer cannot spin scanning megabytes of junk.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Enhance the Existing [0m[1;35mparseHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to Honor headerLookupRange**  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the protected method `[0m[1;35mparseHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString headerMarker, String [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdefaultVersion[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, insert logic to track how many bytes have been consumed from [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`source` and abort if exceeding `headerLookupRange`. For example:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     long startPos = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     String header = [0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     long scanned = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - startPos;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     while [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mheader.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mheaderMarker[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && scanned < headerLookupRange[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         header = [0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         scanned = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - startPos;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mheader.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mheaderMarker[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35msource.seek[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return false;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m existing logic to parse version and rewind [0m[33m...[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This replaces unbounded line-by-line scanning with a bounded scan, directly [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddressing the libFuzzer timeout.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Preserve Existing API Visibility and Call Sites**  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Keep `[0m[1;35mparsePDFHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mparseFDFHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` as protected methods delegating[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto `[0m[1;35mparseHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` so that `PDFParser` and `FDFParser` can still call them [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout visibility issues.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes are needed in `PDFParser.java` or `FDFParser.java`, and all [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructor calls to `[0m[1;35mCOSParser[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` will compile correctly.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Clean Up Imports**  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure only the necessary imports remain [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`import [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mjava.nio.charset.StandardCharsets;` only once[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All other imports [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `Logger`, IO classes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m stay untouched.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **Validate and Test**  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run full Maven build to confirm no compilation errors.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Execute existing PDFBox test suite to verify no regressions.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Re-run libFuzzer harness; confirm that header scanning now completes in [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbounded time without spurious timeouts.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Justification**  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Restoring the public constructors immediately fixes the broken constructor-call [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merrors in `FDFParser` and `PDFParser`.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Removing the duplicate-signed private methods resolves the “method already [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdefined” compilation failures.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- By adding a configurable `headerLookupRange` and bounding the header search in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparseHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, the fuzzer-driven timeouts are addressed while preserving the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moriginal version-parsing logic and API.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No harness or external library code is modified; only the core `COSParser` is [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menhanced. Existing functionality [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding multi-line header parsing and lenient [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mversion fallback[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains intact.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Potential Side Effects & Mitigations**  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Very unusual PDFs with headers beyond the default [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m KB may now fail header [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetection. Users can increase `-Dorg.apache.pdfbox.pdfparser.[0m[33mheaderLookupRange[0m[39m=<N>`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto handle larger edge cases.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- By conservative default [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m KB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, we mitigate most fuzzer hang scenarios while [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mretaining compatibility with standard PDFs.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis strategy cleanly consolidates the header-scan refactoring, removes the faulty [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch remnants, and preserves all existing parsing behavior and public APIs.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe original issue reported by the fuzzer is a libFuzzer timeout when parsing [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcertain PDF inputs, indicating a potential infinite loop or excessively long scan [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the header-parsing logic of COSParser. In response, a patch was proposed that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintroduces a new system property [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`headerLookupRange`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and corresponding limit [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic in the `parseHeader` method to bound how far the parser will scan for the PDF[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mversion header. After applying this patch, the project fails to compile with [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmultiple “cannot find symbol: variable EOF_MARKER” errors in `COSParser.java`.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The only symptom provided is “ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout.”  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No stack trace or code location was given by the fuzzer; it simply indicates that[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe parser did not terminate in a reasonable time when driven by the fuzz harness.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Added a new public system property key [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`org.apache.pdfbox.pdfparser.headerLookupRange`.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Defined a new private field `headerLookupRange` and a default constant [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`DEFAULT_[0m[1;33mHEAD[0m[39mER_LOOKUP_RANGE = 1024L`.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mparseHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString headerMarker, String defaultVersion[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, recorded the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstarting stream position [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`startPos`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and tracked how many bytes have been read [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`scanned`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Wrapped the existing loop that reads lines looking for the header marker with an [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madditional condition `scanned < headerLookupRange`.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Updated assignments of `scanned` inside the loop so that the loop will exit once [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe byte-count limit is reached.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Result  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The build fails during compilation of `COSParser.java`.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The errors reported by Maven:  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m occurrences of “cannot find symbol: variable EOF_MARKER” at lines [0m[1;36m342[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m349[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand [0m[1;36m353[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- These errors indicate that the declaration of `EOF_MARKER` is no longer visible [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto the rest of the class.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImportant Observations and Findings  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The compilation errors all reference the symbol `EOF_MARKER`, which is declared [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mearlier in the file.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. At least one patch hunk modifies the area around the Javadoc comment preceding [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`private static final char[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m EOF_MARKER`.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. The error suggests that the `EOF_MARKER` declaration may have been inadvertently[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremoved, commented out, or shifted out of scope by the patch.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. The lines indicated in the error messages [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line numbers [0m[1;36m342[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m353[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrespond to uses of `EOF_MARKER` in trailer-parsing code later in the file.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe project’s fuzzing harness reports a persistent libFuzzer timeout when [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexercising the PDF parser. An attempted patch augments the `COSParser` class by [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintroducing a configurable byte-range cap [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`headerLookupRange`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m on how far [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`parseHeader` may search for the PDF header marker. After applying the patch, the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame libFuzzer timeout error continues to occur, indicating the change did not [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresolve the hanging behavior.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- When running libFuzzer against the PDFBox codebase, the process consistently [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimes out without completing a parse of certain inputs.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The only log output is the generic “ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout,” which indicates [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe fuzzer did not return control within the allotted time.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- There are no stack traces or specific error messages pointing to a particular [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mline or method, only that the harness reached its execution time limit.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- File modified: `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/COSParser.java` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- New static system property `org.apache.pdfbox.pdfparser.headerLookupRange` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mdefault [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m added.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A new instance field `headerLookupRange` [0m[1;39m([0m[39minitialized to 1024L[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m introduced.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `[0m[1;35mparseHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString headerMarker, String defaultVersion[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Record the starting byte position [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`startPos = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • After reading each line, compute `scanned = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - startPos`.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Loop to read subsequent lines only while the header marker isn’t found **and** [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`scanned` is less than `headerLookupRange`.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Diff Snippet  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+++ b/[0m[33m...[0m[35m/[0m[95mCOSParser.java[0m                                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fuzzing still ends with “ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout.”  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No additional logs or stack traces appear post-patch.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The `parseHeader` method and its interaction with the underlying [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35msource.readLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` implementation—especially whether `[0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` can block [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindefinitely or loop without advancing the position under certain corrupted inputs.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Upstream uses of the `source` object to confirm that `[0m[1;35mgetPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and EOF handling behave as expected on malformed streams.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Any other parsing loops in `COSParser` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor related classes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that may exhibit [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msimilar unbounded behavior on malformed input.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. The fuzz harness entry point to verify whether timeouts can be attributed to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msetup overhead or specific parser code paths rather than harness misconfiguration.[0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m329[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m330[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m331[0m[39m:     * Keep reading until the end of the dictionary object or the file has been[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhit, or until a [0m[32m'/'[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif not, i.e. that the[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m335[0m[39m:     * caller can continue to parse the dictionary at the current position.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m336[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m337[0m[39m:     * @throws IOException if there is a reading error.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m338[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m339[0m[39m:    private boolean [0m[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m340[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m341[0m[39m:        int c = [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m342[0m[39m:        while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mc != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m && c != [0m[32m'/'[0m[39m && c != [0m[32m'>'[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m345[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m to stop when we find endstream or endobj.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m346[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mc == E[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m349[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mc == N[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m351[0m[39m:                    c = [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m352[0m[39m:                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mc == D[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m353[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m355[0m[39m:                        boolean isStream = c == S && [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == T && [0m     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m356[0m[39m:                                && [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == E && [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == A && [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == M;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m357[0m[39m:                        boolean isObj = !isStream && c == O && [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ==[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mB[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m358[0m[39m:                                && [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == J;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m359[0m[39m:                        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39misStream || isObj[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m360[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Identify and isolate the infinite loop in `[0m[1;35mCOSParser.parseHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheaderMarker, String defaultVersion[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  Currently the loop:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Calls `[0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` repeatedly until the header marker is found, a version [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mline beginning with a digit is encountered, or the byte‐range cap [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`headerLookupRange`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is exceeded.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • On EOF, `[0m[1;35mBaseParser.readLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` returns an empty string **without [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madvancing** the file pointer.  Consequently, `[0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` does not [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchange, `scanned` remains constant, and the loop never terminates.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Augment the header‐lookup loop to detect EOF or zero‐advancement and break out. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mSpecifically:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Introduce a variable [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. `long previousPos`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to record the stream position[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimmediately before each `[0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • After calling `[0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and recomputing `scanned = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m -[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstartPos`, compare the new `[0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with `previousPos`.  If the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mposition has not increased [0m[1;39m([0m[39mEOF or non‐advancing read[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, explicitly `break` the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop.[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • This check should be inserted at the start or end of the `while` loop that [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msearches for the header marker.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Example pseudocode patch sketch for `[0m[1;35mparseHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `COSParser.java`:[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private boolean [0m[1;35mparseHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString headerMarker, String defaultVersion[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         long startPos = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         String header = [0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         long scanned = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - startPos;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mheader.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mheaderMarker[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             long previousPos = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             header = [0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             scanned = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - startPos;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             while [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mheader.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mheaderMarker[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && scanned < headerLookupRange[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m break on version line[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mheader.isEmpty[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && [0m[1;35mCharacter.isDigit[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mheader.charAt[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     break;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m break on EOF/non-advancing read[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 long currentPos = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentPos <= previousPos[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                     break;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 previousPos = currentPos;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 header = [0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 scanned = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - startPos;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m existing fallback if marker not found[0m[33m...[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preserve all existing functionality:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Retain the configurable `headerLookupRange` cap and system property support.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Retain the [0m[32m"break on digit-leading line"[0m[39m logic.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Retain lenient vs. strict header‐not‐found behavior and default version [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfallback.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Validate that no harness or test code is modified.  The fix lives entirely in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`COSParser.parseHeader`.  Existing tests [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding fuzz harness[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m continue to call [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`parse` and exercise `parseHeader` unchanged, but the new EOF check prevents the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munbounded loop on malformed inputs.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Run libFuzzer again; confirm that:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • The parser now returns control instead of hanging at EOF.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Timeouts no longer occur on inputs that previously caused hanging in [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`parseHeader`.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • All existing parsing logic beyond the header‐lookup remains unmodified and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpasses existing PDFBox test suites.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mRationale:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The hanging occurred because `[0m[1;35mreadLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` can return an empty string at EOF [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout advancing the stream position, so the loop’s byte‐range guard never trips.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- By explicitly detecting non‐advancing reads, we safely exit the header‐search [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop on EOF, matching how other parser loops [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. `readUntilEndOfCOSDictionary`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetect end‐of‐stream.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This minimal change preserves all existing path logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39mheader marker search, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mversion‐line detection, range cap[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and does not alter harness, fuzzing logic, or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexternal dependencies. [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Side effects are limited to ensuring termination on EOF; any legitimate blank [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlines early in the file still advance the position and are handled normally.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
